\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "thm:激波管：激波：相对马赫数"

\end_inset

流体微团穿过激波是熵增的减速压缩过程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
s_{\mathrm{B}}<s_{\mathrm{A}}\qquad p_{\mathrm{B}}<p_{\mathrm{A}}\qquad\rho_{\mathrm{B}}<\rho_{\mathrm{A}}\qquad T_{\mathrm{B}}<T_{\mathrm{A}}\qquad0<a_{\mathrm{B}}<a_{\mathrm{A}}
\]

\end_inset

速度由超音速减至亚音速：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\abs{v_{\mathrm{B}}}>\abs{v_{\mathrm{A}}}\qquad M_{\mathrm{B}}>1>M_{\mathrm{A}}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $M=\abs{v}/a$
\end_inset

 为“相对马赫数 (relative Mach number)
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
number!Mach ~!relative ~
\end_layout

\end_inset

”。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

