\begin_layout Corollary
右侧为波前（
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{B}=k+\text{、}\mathrm{A}=k-$
\end_inset

）的激波称为“
\bar under
右行 (right-running)
\bar default
 激波”，它只可能是第三特征场（
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{3}=u+a$
\end_inset

